The pins in the parallell port is used as follows:

1       -  Selects left or right channel
2 to 9  -  8 data bits (2 = Least Significant Bit , 9 = Most ...)
14      -  Pin 1 inverted (isn't used in my D/A, but may be useful)
25      -  Ground

